## Installation

```shell
pip install fastapi-debug-toolbar
```

## Quickstart

```py
from debug_toolbar.middleware import DebugToolbarMiddleware
from fastapi import FastAPI

app = FastAPI(debug=True)
app.add_middleware(DebugToolbarMiddleware)
```

